NNNNOOOOTTTTEEEE
     _T_h_e _r._c_n_2 program is sensitive to the ccccuuuurrrrrrrreeeennnntttt wwwwiiiinnnnddddoooowwww sssseeeettttttttiiiinnnngggg.
     Thus  the  program  can  be used to generate a CN map of any
     sub-area within the full map layer. Also, _r._c_n_2 is  sensitive
     to any _m_a_s_k in effect.


